            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <h2 class="text-center text-justify">About Us</h2>
                    <hr class="divider-darkblue">
                    <p>We are a collective of creators and visual storytellers based in Berlin.</p>
                    <p>At Lux Sapiens we use photos and videos to tell stories. Everybody has a story to tell. 
                        And every story has an audience. Our job is to convey your message in a visually pleasing way. </p>
                    <p>Our team has artists specialized in many different areas and medias.</p>
                </div>
